{"tid":2278252,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子去年涉網上售電槍伸縮棍 今被姚勳智法官判囚32個月 指社會活動活躍時期如落入不法分子手上 可致嚴重後果","createTime":"2020-11-09T04:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T06:12:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"95c16fb1a1b066e7662f1e5c089bb93e2de5e75f","tid":2278252,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4285\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F4285&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=fb2a1648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4285</a><br />\n<br />\n無業漢網售伸縮棍電槍判囚32月 官：落入不法分子手後果嚴重<br />\n<br />\n【頭條日報】債台高築的無業漢聲稱無力償還債務，遂在網上出售伸縮棍及電槍等武器，終被警方假扮買家揭發事件。他今承認無牌經營槍械及管有違禁武器兩罪，以換取控方撤銷另一項管有違禁武器控罪，法官表示被告在社會活動活躍時期出售涉案槍械，如落入不法分子手上，可引致嚴重後果，終判囚32個月。（全文 ）<br />\n<br />\n#20201109新聞"},{"pid":"c0d42530e3d2e00a685bfe579d27eefaf043d26c","tid":2278252,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09a1df81f7258854b0f1a8e6442140e93a5177e","tid":2278252,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea8bd80172254f4915e9867688859f33b88b309","tid":2278252,"uid":279357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:05:26.000Z","msg":"撈偏咁易咩<br />\n當交學費啦"},{"pid":"e31ef4bbdcff79a2ef64fefef3585eaed9beb489","tid":2278252,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:19:53.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"55