<br />\n咁不如唔畀用汽油？唔畀用天拿水？唔畀用玻璃樽？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />電槍都算數。伸縮棍係咩事..."},{"pid":"e50de0e289f9a045ba4f14b8d4ca54082d736e7e","tid":2278252,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:10:29.000Z","msg":"惟法官認為，兩罪均為嚴重罪行，首項控罪的12支電槍可發出逾 6000 伏特，專家亦指出電槍可使人昏暈。法官又說，事發於多宗社會事件之後，被告以此作生意招徠，難以想像一旦涉案電槍及伸縮棍流到不法人士手中，會造成嚴重傷害；故就兩罪分別判以 28 個月及 20 個月監禁，第二項控罪的 4 個月刑期分期執行，即共判囚 32 個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E7%B6%B2%E5%94%AE%E9%9B%BB%E6%A7%8D%E4%BC%B8%E7%B8%AE%E6%A3%8D-31-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%AA%8D%E5%85%A9%E7%BD%AA%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-32-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2594%25AE%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%25A7%258D%25E4%25BC%25B8%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E6%25A3%258D-31-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-32-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=b94490b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2594%25AE%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%25A7%258D%25E4%25BC%25B8%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E6%25A3%258D-31-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-32-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%2F&h=c4c0adb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E7%B6%B2%E5%94%AE%E9%9B%BB%E6%A7%8D%E4%BC%B8%E7%B8%AE%E6%A3%8D-31-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%AA%8D%E5%85%A9%E7%BD%AA%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-32-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88/</a>"},{"pid":"e4aed7a3d6c98d8ee22ce80a9349cbe161822540","tid":2278252,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:12:42.000Z